HPI 8611 Nissan Skyline GT-R 1993 JTC Autopolis Winner K. Takahashi/K. Tsuchiya

After retiring in the first round of the 1993 JTC season, Kunimitsu Takahashi & Keiichi Tsuchiya came back to take a win in round 2 at Autopolis in Oita. This would be the high point of the season as 3 more retirements in 1993 meant Takahashi & Tsuchiya would finish in 11th & 12th place in the series.
